<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<!-- Calligraphy Font -->
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<title>Farewell Invitation</title>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #111, #000);
        font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        color: #d4af37;
    }

    .invitation {
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 650px;
        padding: 50px 30px;
        text-align: center;
        background: #000;
        border: 8px double #d4af37;
        border-radius: 25px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.6);
        position: relative;
        animation: glow 3s infinite alternate;
    }

    .invitation::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 15px;
        bottom: 15px;
        left: 15px;
        right: 15px;
        border: 2px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5);
        border-radius: 15px;
    }

    /* ULTRA BIG Calligraphy Title */
    h1 {
        font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive;
        font-size: 90px; /* Bigger */
        margin-bottom: 20px;

        /* Gold Gradient */
        background: linear-gradient(45deg, #d4af37, #ffd700, #fff2a8);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;

        /* Glow */
        text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(212,175,55,0.8),
                     0 0 25px rgba(212,175,55,0.7),
                     0 0 40px rgba(255,215,0,0.6);

        /* Shimmer Animation */
        background-size: 200% auto;
        animation: shine 4s linear infinite;
    }

    @keyframes shine {
        0% { background-position: 0% center; }
        100% { background-position: 200% center; }
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .divider {
        width: 80px;
        height: 2px;
        background: #d4af37;
        margin: 20px auto;
    }

    .content {
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .highlight {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 16px;
        opacity: 0.8;
    }

    @keyframes glow {
        0% { box-shadow: 0 0 10px #d4af37; }
        100% { box-shadow: 0 0 40px #d4af37; }
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="invitation">
    <h1>Farewell Party</h1>
    <h2>With Gratitude & Memories</h2>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="content">
        You are cordially invited to celebrate a memorable evening<br>
        as we bid farewell with joy and cherished moments.
        <br><br>

        <span class="highlight">📅 30 March 2026</span><br>
        <span class="highlight">🕑 2:00 PM – 5:00 PM</span><br>
        <span class="highlight">📍 Sangford School</span>

        <br><br>
        Join us for an evening filled with laughter, memories,<br>
        and heartfelt goodbyes.
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="footer">
        Dress Code: Elegant ✨<br>
        We look forward to your presence
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
